      sideEffects: "GI upset (nausea, diarrhea, abdominal cramping -- usually transient and dose-related), metallic taste, vitamin B12 deficiency with long-term use, lactic acidosis (rare)",
      contra: "eGFR <30 mL/min (contraindicated); eGFR 30-45 (use with caution, do not initiate); acute or chronic metabolic acidosis; hold before iodinated contrast procedures",
